[04-07 16:04:00.197]Talk:pageid, count, talk 11  1  Senna: Being a new player, you must understand the basic of each class and attributes. What you wish to know?  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  2  Regarding Classes  function:000001A50DC024D8  12  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  3  Regarding Attributes  function:000001A50DC024D8  13  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  4  I have understood all  function:000001A50DC024D8  6  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Talk:pageid, count, talk 12  1  Senna: There are 7 basic classes in this game. Each has its unique ways and serves a special purpose in the game. Which would you like to become?  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  2  Regarding Swordsman  function:000001A50DC024D8  14  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  3  Regarding Hunter  function:000001A50DC024D8  15  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  4  Regarding Explorer  function:000001A50DC024D8  17  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  5  Regarding Herbalist  function:000001A50DC024D8  18  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  6  Understood. Let me check out others.  function:000001A50DC024D8  11  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:04:00.198]Talk:pageid, count, talk 13  1  Senna: Each character will have 5 base attributes. Players can increase them accordingly to raise certain aspect of their ability. Each level will reward players with 1 stat point and 1 skill point. Beginner will have 5 stat points to distribute.  
