[04-07 16:04:00.198]Talk:pageid, count, talk 28  1  Well done, it looks like you now have a good grasp at basic combat and also a good idea on how item drops work. Since there is nothing much left to learn from me, why don't you go and look for my friends? If fighting is your cup of tea, seek out Marcusa.
