[04-07 16:04:00.200]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Hi! If you want to get rich, then you will need a "Commerce Permit!" With it you can have more products for commerce trade and also reduce your capital to maximize your profits! Currently, players can only obtain Commerce Permit from Shaitan Trading Post
