[04-07 16:04:01.450]Talk:pageid, count, talk 6  1  Chaos Administrator: Including of Chaos Framestone, Chaos Clawstone, Chaos Pawstone, this set of equipment has high attribute bonus and other hidden ability. These abilities will be activated according to your ranking on the list.  
