[04-07 16:09:53.469]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  Argent City's Blacksmith Goldie deals in the sale of weapons. His weapons are of excellent quality. Go take a look. Blacksmith's shop is at Argent City's top left corner.  
[04-07 16:09:53.469]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  2  Regarding other shops  function:000002120DBFF630  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.469]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  3  I have understood all  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.469]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  Armors made in Argent City are very durable. You can have a look at them at the top right corner of the city.  
[04-07 16:09:53.469]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  2  Regarding other shops  function:000002120DBFF630  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.469]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  3  I have understood all  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Talk:pageid, count, talk 8  1  We have a lot of items here that are important to an Explorer. Check it out on the right side of the pond.  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  2  Regarding other shops  function:000002120DBFF630  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  3  I have understood all  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Talk:pageid, count, talk 9  1  Teleporter can send you to any city in this land. They can also record the spawn point for you. She is beside the western gate.  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  9  2  Regarding other shops  function:000002120DBFF630  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  9  3  I have understood all  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Talk:pageid, count, talk 10  1  The nurse is just slightly below the fountain. She is a gentle and caring lady that is well loved by all.  
