[04-07 16:09:53.470]Talk:pageid, count, talk 12  1  Arena Administrator: Hi, 100 Party Contribution points can be exchanged for 10 Honor points. You also need to pay 5000G and have a negative Honor point value in order to exchange.  
[04-07 16:09:53.470]Talk:pageid, count, talk 13  1  Arena Administrator: Hi, exchanging 300 Party Contribution points for 30 Honor points requires 300 Party Contribution points, 15000G and negative Honor points  
