[04-07 16:09:53.972]Talk:pageid, count, talk 30  1  Resline: To check the coordinates of monsters in game, all you have to do is look for a Drunkyard in Argent City Bar at (2222, 288). He can tell you the coordinates for a fee.  
[04-07 16:09:53.972]Talk:pageid, count, talk 31  1  Resline: Star of Unity is a mysterious accessory from another world. When you equip it, you might be able to activate the power of unity and something unexpected might happen. We are running a trial event "Hoard Exchange". All players below Lv 41 can red
[04-07 16:09:53.972]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  31  2  Redeem Star of Unity  function:000002120DBFF780  table:000002122354C9A8  1  nil  nil  
