[04-07 16:09:53.972]Talk:pageid, count, talk 1  1  Franklin: Hi! I learnt my ship building skill in Argent City. You can call me Franklin.  
[04-07 16:09:53.972]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  1  2  Build Ship  function:000002120DBFF780  table:000002122355F108  1  nil  nil  
