[04-07 16:09:53.972]Talk:pageid, count, talk 2  1  Franklin: Yo! Want to set sail? Then you will need a good ship! Look at my ships and see if there is any to your liking. To level up your ship, come back when it has gained enough experience from sailing or killing monsters out in the sea.  
