[04-07 16:09:53.972]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Franklin: You need to have your ship docked at my harbor in order to level it. Ships get better as they level up. To level up your ship, come back when it has gained enough experience from sailing or killing monsters out in the sea.  
