[04-07 16:09:54.055]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Players can reselect their class after rebirth: Lance can become Champion, Crusader, Voyager or Sharpshooter. Carsise can become Champion. Phyllis can become Crusader, Cleric, Seal Master, Voyager or Sharpshooter. Ami can become Cleric, Seal Master or Vo
[04-07 16:09:54.055]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  3  2  Thank you, I understand  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:54.055]Talk:pageid, count, talk 4  1  All attributes will be resetted upon rebirth and all additional stat points gained from Career Lot or Birthday Cake will remained for reallocation. Also, all skill will be resetted and skill points will be returned for reallocation.  
[04-07 16:09:54.055]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  2  Thank you, I understand  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:54.055]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  To be rebirth, you will need to complete quest Phoenix Rebirth which can be activated at the Goddess. Look for me after you obtained the Rebirth Stone or you can come directly to me if you have the Rebirth Card.  
