[04-07 16:09:54.488]?????NPC??Icicle Swordsman - Ray????????????? 
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 1  1  Ray: I am a bounty hunter. I love to hunt for undeads. If you are interested, I can recommend a few places to you.  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 2  1  Hi my friend. You have great reflexes, suitable to become a hunter. Why don't you become a hunter now? I believe that you will not be disappointed.  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  2  2  Ok, class change to be Hunter  function:000002120DBFF780  table:000002123829B530  2  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  2  3  No, it is good enough for now.  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  I have told you all I can about being a Hunter. Now its up to you to become the best Hunter.  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 4  1  Want to be a Hunter? Only players Lv 8 and above who possess a Hunter Manual can register with me for 1000G. Muscular guy or little girl are not suitable.  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  Sharpshoots nowadays only want to earn more money. They will kill anyone on sight as long as there is a bounty. Friend, it seems that you are suitable to become a sharpshooter. You have a good character and build. Would you consider to be one so that you
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  2  Ok, I will become a Sharpshooter  function:000002120DBFF780  table:000002123829F560  2  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  3  No, it is good enough for now.  function:000002120DBFF690  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 6  1  Sharpshooters are not assassins. You must not forget the principles of the sharpshooters in the future.  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  Want to become a Sharpshooter? Come back here when you are Lv 40. Remember to bring along 1 Clarity Crystal and 15000G too!  
