[04-07 16:09:54.488]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  Reyno: Those herbs sold by physicians are just common herbs. Only I possess rare herbs that do miracles.  
[04-07 16:09:54.488]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  2  Make Agrypnotic  function:000002120DBFF780  table:00000212382B4738  1  nil  nil  
