[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 1  1  Salvier: Hi! You look new! How can I help you?  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  1  2  Who are you?  function:000001688DC10D00  2  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  1  3  Where is this place?  function:000001688DC10D00  3  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  1  4  I think I have understand. Goodbye  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 2  1  Salvier: I am in charge of answering people's question for this city. If you meet up with any trouble, look for me.  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  2  2  Return  function:000001688DC10D00  1  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Salvier: This is the most prosperous city in the whole of Ascaron. We have no lack of resources in any way. This is all thanks to our Duke who built this city.  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  3  2  Return  function:000001688DC10D00  1  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 4  1  Salvier: Ok sure, look for me again if you need more.  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  2  Ok, I want to know some more things.  function:000001688DC10D00  5  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  Salvier: Don't be shy. Ask away.  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  2  The Duke and founding of Argent  function:000001688DC10D00  6  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 6  1  Salvier: Many centuries ago, a war between the demons and Ascaron empire ensures. It lasted for years and taken a hugh toll on the citizen of the empire. Due to this, the Duke and his nephew leads the citizen to the current Argent City and build it from 
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  Salvier: As a great leader of a great city, I will treat all newcomers with hospitality. A gift of  100G! You can receive healing from the nurse if you are below Lv 5 too!  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  2  Thank you!  function:000001688DC10E50  table:000001688DFCAEF8  1  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Talk:pageid, count, talk 8  1  Salvier: Hi! Argent City need someone like you!  
[04-07 16:21:24.411]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  2  Thank you. I am only looking around  function:000001688DC10D60  nil  nil  nil  nil  
