[04-07 16:21:24.415]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  1  3  Regarding High Lv Commerce Permit  function:000001688DC10D00  3  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Talk:pageid, count, talk 2  1  Chiroro: Sorry, you do not have any ships docked in Argent Harbor . Unable to trade.  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Hi! If you want to get rich, then you will need a "Commerce Permit!" With it you can have more products for commerce trade and also reduce your capital to maximize your profits! Currently, players can only obtain Commerce Permit from Shaitan Trading Post
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  3  2  Regarding Tax Rate  function:000001688DC10D00  7  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  3  3  Low Lv Commerce Permit  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  3  4  Mid Lv Commerce Permit  function:000001688DC10D00  5  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  3  5  High Lv Commerce Permit  function:000001688DC10D00  6  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Talk:pageid, count, talk 4  1  Low Lv Commerce Permit is easy to obtain. When you reaches Lv 20, go to the trading post in Shaitan and complete a simple task to have one.  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  When you reaches Lv 40 and reduces your tax rate to 20, you can go to Shaitan Trading Post and obtain a Mid Lv Commerce Permit.  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Talk:pageid, count, talk 6  1  When you have reached level 60 and possess a Commerce Permit with 10 0x0.0000000000000p+0x, you can activate the quest for High Lv Commerce.  
[04-07 16:21:24.415]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  Check your Commerce Permit to see the current Tax Rate imposed on your product when you sell it to any trader. Complete some quest at Shaitan Trading Post to reduce the Tax Rate.  
