[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 4  1  Argent City is a place for merchant to sell their products. Have a look around.  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  2  Regarding Weapon Shop  function:000001688DC10D00  5  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  3  Regarding Armor Shop  function:000001688DC10D00  7  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  4  Regarding Item Shop  function:000001688DC10D00  8  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  5  Regarding Teleporter  function:000001688DC10D00  9  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  6  Regarding the Nurse  function:000001688DC10D00  10  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  Argent City's Blacksmith Goldie deals in the sale of weapons. His weapons are of excellent quality. Go take a look. Blacksmith's shop is at Argent City's top left corner.  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  2  Regarding other shops  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  3  I have understood all  function:000001688DC10D60  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  Armors made in Argent City are very durable. You can have a look at them at the top right corner of the city.  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  2  Regarding other shops  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  3  I have understood all  function:000001688DC10D60  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 8  1  We have a lot of items here that are important to an Explorer. Check it out on the right side of the pond.  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  2  Regarding other shops  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  3  I have understood all  function:000001688DC10D60  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 9  1  Teleporter can send you to any city in this land. They can also record the spawn point for you. She is beside the western gate.  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  9  2  Regarding other shops  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  9  3  I have understood all  function:000001688DC10D60  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 10  1  The nurse is just slightly below the fountain. She is a gentle and caring lady that is well loved by all.  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  10  2  Regarding other shops  function:000001688DC10D00  4  nil  nil  nil  
