[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 11  1  Senna: Being a new player, you must understand the basic of each class and attributes. What you wish to know?  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  2  Regarding Classes  function:000001688DC10D00  12  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.420]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  3  Regarding Attributes  function:000001688DC10D00  13  nil  nil  nil  
