[04-07 16:21:24.420]Talk:pageid, count, talk 13  1  Senna: Each character will have 5 base attributes. Players can increase them accordingly to raise certain aspect of their ability. Each level will reward players with 1 stat point and 1 skill point. Beginner will have 5 stat points to distribute.  
