[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  Arena Administrator: Each battle will increase battle count by 1  
[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 8  1  Arena Administrator: Each kill will increase Kill count by 1 and 1 Honor point (Opponent lower by 10 levels will not have any Honor. Those higher by 10 levels will earn a bonus 1 Honor). Vice versa for those defeated in challenge.  
[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 9  1  Arena Administrator: Each victory to the party will increase victory count by 1 and gain Honor points according to the differences between the average level of the two parties.  
[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 10  1  Arena Administrator: Each time a party escape or quit battle, System will deduct Honor points according to the average level of both party and an additional of 2 Honor points per person. The other party will gain Honor points based on those lost by the p
[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 11  1  Arena Administrator: Hi! To exchange 50 Party Contribution points for 5 Honor points, you will need to have 50 Party Contribution points, 2500G and a negative Honor value.  
[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 12  1  Arena Administrator: Hi, 100 Party Contribution points can be exchanged for 10 Honor points. You also need to pay 5000G and have a negative Honor point value in order to exchange.  
[04-07 16:21:24.426]Talk:pageid, count, talk 13  1  Arena Administrator: Hi, exchanging 300 Party Contribution points for 30 Honor points requires 300 Party Contribution points, 15000G and negative Honor points  
