[04-07 16:21:24.947]Talk:pageid, count, talk 11  1  Resline: To be a good player, you will need to understand the basic of different classes and attributes. Would you like to find out more?  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  2  Regarding Classes  function:000001688DC10D00  12  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  11  3  Regarding Attributes  function:000001688DC10D00  13  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Talk:pageid, count, talk 12  1  Resline: There are 7 basic classes in this game. Each has its unique ways and serve a special purpose in the game. Which would you like to become?  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  2  Regarding Swordsman  function:000001688DC10D00  14  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  3  Regarding Hunter  function:000001688DC10D00  15  nil  nil  nil  
