[04-07 16:21:24.947]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  12  5  Regarding Herbalist  function:000001688DC10D00  18  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Talk:pageid, count, talk 13  1  Resline: Each character will have 5 base attributes. Players can increase them accordingly to raise certain aspect of their ability. Each level will reward players with 1 stat point and 1 skill point. Beginner will have 5 stat points to distribute.  
[04-07 16:21:24.947]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  13  2  Regarding Strength  function:000001688DC10D00  21  nil  nil  nil  
