[04-07 16:21:25.033]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Players can reselect their class after rebirth: Lance can become Champion, Crusader, Voyager or Sharpshooter. Carsise can become Champion. Phyllis can become Crusader, Cleric, Seal Master, Voyager or Sharpshooter. Ami can become Cleric, Seal Master or Vo
