[04-07 16:27:38.117]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  2  2  Return  function:0000023345C6F7E8  1  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:38.117]Talk:pageid, count, talk 3  1  Salvier: This is the most prosperous city in the whole of Ascaron. We have no lack of resources in any way. This is all thanks to our Duke who built this city.  
