[04-07 16:27:39.148]Talk:pageid, count, talk 4  1  Just like what you have seen, Icicle City is a place covered in snow. To stay here in comfort, you must learn how to get the necessary items and equipments.  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  2  Regarding Weapon Shop  function:0000023345C6F7E8  5  nil  nil  nil  
