[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  4  Regarding Item Shop  function:0000023345C6F7E8  8  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  5  Regarding Teleporter  function:0000023345C6F7E8  9  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  4  6  Regarding Healing  function:0000023345C6F7E8  10  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Talk:pageid, count, talk 5  1  Walk south from here and turn right at the crossroad. From there, you should be able to see the Blacksmith. He sell all sort of weapons. See if you can find anything you like.  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  2  Regarding other shops  function:0000023345C6F7E8  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  5  3  I have understood all  function:0000023345C6F848  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Talk:pageid, count, talk 7  1  To buy armors, look for the Tailor. He is a friendly and kind man. Find him at the bottom right corner of town.  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  2  Regarding other shops  function:0000023345C6F7E8  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  7  3  I have understood all  function:0000023345C6F848  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Talk:pageid, count, talk 8  1  Buying items? The grocery is not far from here. It is at the western corner of this city. It will have all you need to start your adventure.  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  2  Regarding other shops  function:0000023345C6F7E8  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  8  3  I have understood all  function:0000023345C6F848  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Talk:pageid, count, talk 9  1  Walk along the path and you will find a beautiful lady near the gate. She is the Teleporter who can send you to other cities. You can also record your Spawn point there.  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  9  2  Regarding other shops  function:0000023345C6F7E8  4  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  9  3  I have understood all  function:0000023345C6F848  nil  nil  nil  nil  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Talk:pageid, count, talk 10  1  The nurse is the lady at the other side of the fountain. Remember to look for her when you are sick or injuired.  
[04-07 16:27:39.148]Text:pageid, count, text, func, p1, p2, p3, p4  10  2  Regarding other shops  function:0000023345C6F7E8  4  nil  nil  nil  
